another one of your messes.

525
00:36:08.320 --> 00:36:11.190
Speaking of messes. have
you seen our missing foreman?

526
00:36:13.159 --> 00:36:14.827
Eh.

527
00:36:14.927 --> 00:36:17.296
Chet always was a lousy shot.

528
00:36:21.567 --> 00:36:23.803
You should've
finished me yourself.

529
00:36:23.936 --> 00:36:26.005
'cause you're never getting
another chance.

530
00:36:26.839 --> 00:36:29.776
I got more chances than
a rattlesnake in a henhouse.

531
00:36:29.842 --> 00:36:31.911
Excuse me. Mr. Reyes?

532
00:36:31.978 --> 00:36:33.379
You're good to go.

533
00:36:34.146 --> 00:36:36.182
<i>Bienvenidos.</i> motherfucker.

534
00:36:36.315 --> 00:36:37.984
Fuck's sake.

535
00:36:38.084 --> 00:36:39.719
Learn Spanish already.

536
00:36:51.397 --> 00:36:52.765
<i>I give you a deal.</i>

537
00:36:52.832 --> 00:36:55.167
and all of a sudden.
you decide to retire?

538
00:36:55.267 --> 00:36:56.936
I'm a ranch girl. Zane.

539
00:36:57.036 --> 00:36:59.505
Beth and Rip are the brains
behind the operation.

540
00:36:59.605 --> 00:37:01.473
You sold me on you.

541
00:37:01.573 --> 00:37:06.045
I'm selling the story of you.
not just your ranch.

542
00:37:06.145 --> 00:37:07.179
Come. dear.

543
00:37:07.279 --> 00:37:09.381
You're gonna love my son.

544
00:37:09.515 --> 00:37:10.649
He's the real deal.

545
00:37:10.717 --> 00:37:12.518
Your son's a drug addict.

546
00:37:14.386 --> 00:37:15.688
Oh. my God.

547
00:37:15.788 --> 00:37:17.123
Put that down!

548
00:37:19.759 --> 00:37:21.861
Carter. what the fuck?

549
00:37:23.629 --> 00:37:24.864
Shit.

550
00:37:24.997 --> 00:37:26.632
That's bad business. kid.

551
00:37:29.001 --> 00:37:31.537
Hey. What the fuck
are you doing?

552
00:37:41.881 --> 00:37:43.515
Help!

553
00:37:46.085 --> 00:37:48.420
- Shit.
- Get him out of here.

554
00:37:49.521 --> 00:37:51.357
- It's okay.
- It's okay. darling.

555
00:37:59.065 --> 00:38:00.599
Yeah. it's Dr. McKinney.
I need a medevac.

556
00:38:00.699 --> 00:38:02.935
10-Petal Ranch. main house.
right now.

557
00:38:03.770 --> 00:38:06.405
Okay.
Look at me. Look at me.

558
00:38:06.538 --> 00:38:08.474
You'll be okay.

559
00:38:10.076 --> 00:38:11.577
Hang in there.

560
00:38:11.710 --> 00:38:12.912
Hang in there. B.

561
00:38:13.012 --> 00:38:15.281
Help's coming.

562
00:38:15.414 --> 00:38:16.515
Hang on. B. It's okay.

563
00:38:23.455 --> 00:38:25.391
Stay with me.

564
00:38:33.699 --> 00:38:35.067
Yes?

565
00:38:35.134 --> 00:38:36.668
Can I come in?

566
00:38:45.177 --> 00:38:46.545
Your father wants you downstairs
for his speech.

567
00:38:46.612 --> 00:38:47.980
He's been waiting.

568
00:38:49.215 --> 00:38:51.683
I'm done
with his fucking speeches.

569
00:38:52.551 --> 00:38:56.355
Hey. B. it's okay.

570
00:39:14.206 --> 00:39:15.641
Drive me somewhere?

571
00:39:32.458 --> 00:39:34.060
You sure?

572
00:39:35.294 --> 00:39:37.196
He deserves to know
he's gonna be a father.

573
00:39:37.296 --> 00:39:39.899
I'm right here if you need me.

574
00:40:04.023 --> 00:40:06.025
- Hey.
- Mind if I come in?

575
00:40:06.158 --> 00:40:07.526
Yeah. come on in.

576
00:40:38.891 --> 00:40:40.726
Found my other boot.
